    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior presents well, though it does show some minor signs of age such as small stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the interior is clean and comfortable, with all electronic features and climate control working as they should. It drives smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable choice for a daily driver. You can expect a dependable vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
